butools.trace.IATimesFromCummulative¶

butools.trace.IATimesFromCummulative()¶
Matlab: iat = IATimesFromCummulative(trace)
Mathematica: iat = IATimesFromCummulative[trace]
Python/Numpy: iat = IATimesFromCummulative(trace)

Returns the vector of inter-arrival times of a trace containing cummulative data.

Parameters:

trace : vector of doubles

The trace data (cummulative)
Returns:

iat : vector of doubles

The inter-arrival times
